{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8a7b9c6d-5e4f-3a2b-1c0d-9e8f7a6b5c4d",
    "name": "Bancard vPOS Backend API",
    "description": "Colección completa para interactuar y probar el backend vPOS de Bancard.\n\n### Auditoría en Base de Datos\nCada vez que llamas a `/api/pagosimple`, el sistema guarda un registro en la tabla `pago_simple_audits` en tu base de datos MySQL (con AWS RDS). \n\n**Queries útiles para probar la base de datos:**\n```sql\n-- Ver los últimos pagos registrados:\nSELECT * FROM pago_simple_audits ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 10;\n\n-- Buscar pagos de un servicio específico:\nSELECT * FROM pago_simple_audits WHERE servicio = 'boletos/custodia';\n\n-- Buscar por el process ID:\nSELECT * FROM pago_simple_audits WHERE shop_process_id = '103';\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Pago Simple (Gateway Unificado)",
      "description": "Endpoints que centralizan toda la comunicación desde el Frontend Externo usando la acción correspondiente.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.a Iniciar Pago (single-buy)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"action\": \"single-buy\",\n    \"shopProcessId\": {{$randomInt}},\n    \"amount\": 25000,\n    \"currency\": \"PYG\",\n    \"description\": \"Compra de Boleto de Custodia\",\n    \"servicio\": \"boletos/custodia\",\n    \"canal\": \"totem/web/puntodeventa\",\n    \"id\": \"BOLETO-EXT-1001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/pagosimple",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pagosimple"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Inicia un pago simple, genera el processId de Bancard y la URL de redirección, y registra la auditoría en la base de datos."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "1.b Revertir Pago (rollback)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"action\": \"rollback\",\n    \"shopProcessId\": 103,\n    \"servicio\": \"boletos/custodia\",\n    \"canal\": \"totem/web/puntodeventa\",\n    \"id\": \"BOLETO-EXT-1001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/pagosimple",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pagosimple"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cancela/reerte un pago pendiente usando el Gateway de Pago Simple. Registra la auditoría correspondiente."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "1.c Consultar Estado (confirmation)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"action\": \"confirmation\",\n    \"shopProcessId\": 103,\n    \"servicio\": \"boletos/custodia\",\n    \"canal\": \"totem/web/puntodeventa\",\n    \"id\": \"BOLETO-EXT-1001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/pagosimple",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pagosimple"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Consulta el estado final del pago (aprobado/rechazado) utilizando el Gateway de Pago Simple. Registra la auditoría en la base de datos."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "1.d Devolución (charge-back)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"action\": \"charge-back\",\n    \"shopProcessId\": 103,\n    \"amount\": 25000,\n    \"currency\": \"PYG\",\n    \"servicio\": \"boletos/custodia\",\n    \"canal\": \"totem/web/puntodeventa\",\n    \"id\": \"BOLETO-EXT-1001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/pagosimple",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pagosimple"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve o contracarga el dinero cobrado a un cliente mediante el Gateway de Pago Simple. Registra la auditoría en la base de datos."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Bancard Operaciones Directas (Puras)",
